"1 pound (16 cups) bakery white bread, cut into 1-inch cubes","1/4 cup extra-virgin olive oil","1 pound sliced applewood-smoked bacon, cut into 1/2-inch pieces","1  (large) onion, halved and thinly sliced","28 ounces (1 can) whole Italian tomatoes, drained, chopped and patted dry","1/2 teaspoon crushed red pepper","1/2 pound (about 2 cups) extra-sharp cheddar, shredded","1/2 pound (about 2 cups) Monterey Jack cheese, shredded","2 tablespoons chives, snipped","1 3/4 cups low-sodium chicken broth","  Salt","8  (large) eggs","  Hot sauce, for serving"